def is_vegetable(x: item):
    # Function to determine if an item is a vegetable
    return is_food_vegetable(x)

def find_sink_for_washing():
    # Function to find a sink suitable for washing vegetables
    foreach o: item:
        if is_sink(o) and not visited(o):
            observe(o, "Check if the sink is available for washing vegetables")

behavior clean_vegetable(vegetable: item, sink: item):
    body:
        achieve_once inside(vegetable, sink)
        if exists faucet: item: is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink)
            achieve_once is_on(faucet)
            wash(vegetable)
            achieve_once is_off(faucet)
        else:
            wash(vegetable)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind sink: item where:
            is_sink(sink)
        foreach vegetable: item:
            if is_vegetable(vegetable) and dirty(vegetable):
                clean_vegetable(vegetable, sink)
